quran[6{c,v,t}:
12,38,"apne buzurgon, ibrahim, ishaq aur yaqoob ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya hai hamara yeh kaam nahi hai ke Allah ke sath kisi ko shareektehraئیں Dur haqeeqat yeh Allah ka fazl hai hum par aur tamam insanon par ( ke is ne apne siwa kisi ka bandah hamein nahi banaya ) magar aksar log shukar nahi karte"
12,39,"ae zandan ke ساتھیو, tum khud hi socho ke bohat se mutafarraq rab behtar hain ya woh aik Allah jo sab ghalib hai ?"
12,40,"uss ko chore kar tum jin ki bandagi kar rahay ho woh is ke siwa kuch nahi hain ke bas chand naam hain jo tum ne aur tumahray abao ajdaad ne rakh liye hain, Allah ne un ke liye koi sanad nazil nahi ki farmaa rawai ka Iqtidaar Allah ke siwa kisi ke liye nahi hai is ka hukum hai ke khud is ke siwa tum kisi ki bandagi nah karo yahi theth seedha tareeq zindagi hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
12,41,"ae zandan ke sathiyo, tumahray khawab ki tabeer yeh hai ke tum mein se aik to apne rab ( Shah misar ) ko sharaab pilaaye ga, raha dosra to usay suli par charhaya jaye ga aur parinday is ka sir noch noch kar khayen ge faisla ho gaya uss baat ka jo tum pooch rahay thay """
12,42,"phir unn mein se jis ke mutaliq khayaal tha ke woh raha ho jaye ga is se yousuf ne kaha ke"" apne rab ( Shah misar ) se mera zikar karna"" magar shetan ne usay aisa ghaflat mein dala ke woh apne rab ( Shah misar ) se is ka zikar karna bhool gaya aur yousuf kayi saal qaid khanaay mein para raha"
12,43,"aik roz badshah ne kaha"" mein ne khawab mein dekha hai ke saat mouti ghaein hain jin ko saat dubli ghaein kha rahi hain, aur anaaj ki saat balen hari hain aur doosri saat sookhi ae ahal darbaar, mujhe is khawab ki tabeer batao agar tum khowaboon ka matlab samajte ho """
